{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"7":"Fasting"},"section_detail":{"7":{"hadithnumber_first":1638,"hadithnumber_last":1782,"arabicnumber_first":1638,"arabicnumber_last":1782}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1733,"arabicnumber":1733,"text":"حدثنا ابو بكر بن ابي شيبة، حدثنا يزيد بن هارون، عن ابن ابي ذيب، عن الزهري، عن عروة، عن عايشة، قالت: كان رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم يصوم عاشوراء، ويامر بصيامه","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Bukhari And Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":96}}]}